1. *Delu* je već sada u životu postigao mnogo uspeha. (He has already achieved much success in life.)

2. On je spreman da *delu* za bolje sutra. (He is ready to work for a better tomorrow.)

3. Njegova porodica je prihvatila njegovo *delo* bez rezervi. (His family accepted his work without reservations.)

4. On je sposoban da *delu* samostalno. (He is able to work independently.)

5. Naš tim se trudi da *dele* našu viziju. (Our team is striving to share our vision.)

6. *Delu* se na mestu gde se većina ljudi usuđuje da pomisli. (He works in a place where most people dare to think.)